#+begin_quote
[!quote]+ Highlight ([[zotero://open-pdf/library/items/WP66FEUA?page=232&annotation=NQS8AJMC][Page 232]]) Animalization is the process of portraying particular human out-groups as having "negative" nonhuman animal characteristics, which thereby demeans the human groups and treats them as "inferior" to the human in-groups. #D√©finitions
#+end_quote

#+begin_quote
